Cc: Jiri Olsa <jolsa@redhat.com>
Cc: stable@vger.kernel.org      # v5.3+
Link: http://lore.kernel.org/lkml/20210521092053.25683-4-adrian.hunter@intel.com
Signed-off-by: Arnaldo Carvalho de Melo <acme@redhat.com>
